<strong>Bonethunder Staff</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">2H Blunt</a><BR>
Damage per second - 5.28<BR>
Damage 9 - Delay 36<BR>
Weight: 9.9 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/cleric/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/paladin/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">PAL</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/ward_undead.shtml?spellID=228">Ward Undead</a><BR>
Charges: 1<BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(WIS +3) </font>
<BR>
Obtained through the <a href="/quests/bonethunder_staff.shtml?questID=86">Bonethunder Staff</a> quest<BR>

